        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"582628\">@Daniel Almeida</span> usually I would like to create an issue for work like this, it's more clear in that way to list out things you would need to do. Do you want to create an issue based on Benno's notes?</p>\n<p>Changes needed for data in <code>Mutex&lt;T&gt;</code> are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>in the <code>new</code> use <code>impl PinInit&lt;T&gt;</code> instead <code>T</code></li>\n<li>the guard needs to only implement <code>DerefMut</code> if <code>T: Unpin</code></li>\n<li>the guard needs to have <code>fn as_mut(&amp;mut self) -&gt; Pin&lt;&amp;mut T&gt;</code></li>\n</ul>",
